{"ud1.3:0.1":"Udana 1.3 ","ud1.3:0.2":"Tatiyabodhisutta ","ud1.3:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","ud1.3:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava uruvelayam viharati najja neranjaraya tire bodhirukkhamule pathamabhisambuddho. ","ud1.3:1.3":"Tena kho pana samayena bhagava sattaham ekapallankena nisinno hoti vimuttisukhapatisamvedi. ","ud1.3:1.4":"Atha kho bhagava tassa sattahassa accayena tamha samadhimha vutthahitva rattiya pacchimam yamam paticcasamuppadam anulomapatilomam sadhukam manasakasi: ","ud1.3:2.1":"“Iti imasmim sati idam hoti, imassuppada idam uppajjati, ","ud1.3:2.2":"imasmim asati idam na hoti, imassa nirodha idam nirujjhati; yadidam—","ud1.3:2.3":"avijjapaccaya sankhara, ","ud1.3:2.4":"sankharapaccaya vinnanam, ","ud1.3:2.5":"vinnanapaccaya namarupam, ","ud1.3:2.6":"namarupapaccaya salayatanam, ","ud1.3:2.7":"salayatanapaccaya phasso, ","ud1.3:2.8":"phassapaccaya vedana, ","ud1.3:2.9":"vedanapaccaya tanha, ","ud1.3:2.10":"tanhapaccaya upadanam, ","ud1.3:2.11":"upadanapaccaya bhavo, ","ud1.3:2.12":"bhavapaccaya jati, ","ud1.3:2.13":"jatipaccaya jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa sambhavanti. ","ud1.3:2.14":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","ud1.3:3.1":"Avijjaya tveva asesaviraganirodha sankharanirodho, ","ud1.3:3.2":"sankharanirodha vinnananirodho, ","ud1.3:3.3":"vinnananirodha namarupanirodho, ","ud1.3:3.4":"namarupanirodha salayatananirodho, ","ud1.3:3.5":"salayatananirodha phassanirodho, ","ud1.3:3.6":"phassanirodha vedananirodho, ","ud1.3:3.7":"vedananirodha tanhanirodho, ","ud1.3:3.8":"tanhanirodha upadananirodho, ","ud1.3:3.9":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho, ","ud1.3:3.10":"bhavanirodha jatinirodho, ","ud1.3:3.11":"jatinirodha jaramaranam sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupayasa nirujjhanti. ","ud1.3:3.12":"Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti”ti. ","ud1.3:4.1":"Atha kho bhagava etamattham viditva tayam velayam imam udanam udanesi: ","ud1.3:5.1":"“Yada have patubhavanti dhamma, ","ud1.3:5.2":"Atapino jhayato brahmanassa; ","ud1.3:5.3":"Vidhupayam titthati marasenam, ","ud1.3:5.4":"Suriyova obhasayamantalikkhan”ti. ","ud1.3:5.5":"Tatiyam. "}